"{\"uid\": \"politico.eu-article-france-emmanuel-macron-meets-elon-musk-worlds-top-executives-amid-political-turmoil-olympics-investment-business\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"French president will use the occasion to pursue his charm offensive among foreign investors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS - French President Emmanuel Macron on Thursday will host a lunch for some of the world's most influential executives to reassure them that France is still a top investment destination.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9863500835439063, \"rank\": 0.013803940451775455, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Elys\\u00e9e, Macron will dine with some 40 top executives including Tesla's Elon Musk, Coca-Cola's James Quincey, Alibaba's Joe Tsai, Airbnb's Brian Chesky